MacOS Build Instructions
------------------

Setup:

build-tree
	alsp_src
	mwbuild - containing "alspro PPC.lib"
	tcltk_interface
	alsdev

mozart
	Tcl/Tk Folder
		tcl8.0
		tk8.0


Build:

Open mac_alsdev.mcp
Make "PPC Build" to create "ALS Prolog IDE"

Run:

ALS Prolog IDE
alsdir
	builtins
	libraries
	shared
		als_tklib.tcl
		tcltk.pro
		turnstile_splash.gif